{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"title":"Sponge","content":["Preheat oven to 190°C. Grease and line base of a rectangular baking tin (approx. 30 cm x 20 cm x 5 cm).","Place butter in mixing bowl and melt <b>2 min\/80°C\/speed 1<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula and, if necessary, melt again <b>30 sec\/80°C\/speed 1<b>. Transfer to a bowl and set aside."," <strong>Insert butterfly whisk<\/strong>. Place eggs and sugar in mixing bowl then whisk <b>5 min\/speed 3<b>.","Add milk, reserved melted butter and vanilla extract then mix <b>4 sec\/speed 3<b>.","Add flour, baking powder and salt then mix <b>20 sec\/speed 3<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula then mix again <b>10 sec\/speed 3<b>. <strong>Remove butterfly whisk<\/strong>. Transfer to prepared tin then bake for 22-25 minutes (190°C) until golden. Meanwhile, clean mixing bowl and make topping."]},{"title":"Topping","content":["Place butter in mixing bowl and melt <b>2 min\/80°C\/speed 1<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula and, if necessary, melt again <b>30 sec\/80°C\/speed 1<b>.","Add sugar and milk then heat <b>3 min\/100°C\/speed 2<b>.","Add coconut then mix <b>10 sec\/speed 3<b>. After sponge has been cooking for 22-25 minutes, pour over topping. Increase oven temperature to 200°C then bake for a further 10 minutes (200°C).","Leave to cool in tin for 5 minutes before removing. Cool completely on a wire rack before serving in slices."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"Sponge","content":["100 g unsalted butter, diced, plus extra for greasing","3 large eggs","250 g caster sugar","100 g milk","1 tsp vanilla extract","250 g plain flour","2 tsp baking powder","1 pinch fine sea salt"]},{"title":"Topping","content":["125 g unsalted butter, diced","200 g light brown sugar","50 g milk","100 g desiccated coconut"]}],"id":"r267441","imageLink":"https:\/\/2.bp.blogspot.com\/-qH5rUB_wAtI\/XZWqPS5CruI\/AAAAAAAAfVE\/FBf0PSkFwGsVCMoxTTx82Vs-VEsEzSevgCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_G9nZCWi3T3_VUkGg.png","title":"Danish Dream Cake","publishedAt":"2018-01-08T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"3.9 g","fat":"17 g","uom":"per 1 slice","carbohydrates":"42 g","calories":"1464 kJ \/ 349 kcal"},"usefulItems":"wire rack, rectangular baking tin (approx. 30 cm x 20 cm x 5 cm), baking paper, oven","basicInfo":["easy","10m","55m","16 slices"]}